public abstract class ArchivedGraphElementStore<T extends GraphElement> extends GraphElementStore<T> implements com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.loading.Unloadable, com.telenav.kivakit.core.registry.RegistryTrait
Base class for various kinds of attribute stores that are stored in GraphArchives. Archived stores are lazy-loaded, but can be forced partly or entirely into memory by calling loadAll() or loadAllExcept(AttributeSet). Loading of attributes is performed by an associated AttributeLoader which uses AttributeReferences manage individual attributes. Archived stores can be unloaded from memory by calling the method unload() and the attached GraphArchive can be retrieved by subclasses with archive().
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
